    <Statements>
      <Statement>Find all factor pairs for a whole number in the range 1&amp;ndash;100. Recognize that a whole number is a multiple of each of its factors. Determine whether a given whole number in the range 1&amp;ndash;100 is a multiple of a given one-digit number. Determine whether a given whole number in the range 1&amp;ndash;100 is prime or composite.</Statement>
